<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Service Invitation Created</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .email-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B46C1 0%, #9333EA 100%);
            padding: 30px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #6B46C1;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .header-title {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .main-message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .service-card {
            background-color: #F8FAFC;
            border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .service-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1F2937;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .service-detail {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .service-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6B7280;
            min-width: 100px;
        }

        .service-value {
            color: #374151;
        }

        .next-steps {
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .next-steps h3 {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1F2937;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .steps-list {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .steps-list li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #374151;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .cta-button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B46C1 0%, #9333EA 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #F9FAFB;
            padding: 24px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
        }

        .footer-text {
            color: #6B7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .footer-links {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .footer-link {
            color: #6B46C1;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .copyright {
            margin-top: 15px;
            color: #9CA3AF;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 10px;
            }

            .header,
            .content,
            .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .service-card {
                padding: 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="logo-icon">G</div>
                <div class="logo-text">GradPal</div>
            </div>
            <h1 class="header-title">Service Invitation Created</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello Team,
            </div>

            <div class="main-message">
                Great news! A new autonomous service invitation has been successfully created and is ready for
                distribution. This service will help enhance the learning experience for students.
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-title">{{serviceTitle}}</div>

                <div class="service-detail">
                    <div class="service-label">Created by:</div>
                    <div class="service-value">{{teacherName}}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-detail">
                    <div class="service-label">Subject:</div>
                    <div class="service-value">{{subject}}</div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-detail">
                    <div class="service-label">Status:</div>
                    <div class="service-value">Ready to Send</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>What happens next:</h3>
                <ul class="steps-list">
                    <li>The invitation will be distributed to selected participants</li>
                    <li>Recipients will receive detailed service information</li>
                    <li>Service will activate once participants accept</li>
                    <li>You'll receive updates on invitation responses</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="main-message">
                This service is designed to provide personalized learning experiences and support educational goals.
                We're excited to see the positive impact it will have on the learning community.
            </div>

            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="#" class="cta-button">View Service Details</a>
            </div>

            <div class="main-message">
                <strong>Need assistance?</strong><br>
                Our support team is here to help with any questions about the service setup or invitation process.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-text">This is an automated notification from GradPal.</div>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">www.gradpal.io</a>
                <a href="#" class="footer-link">support@gradpal.io</a>
            </div>
            <div class="copyright">Â© 2025 GradPal. All rights reserved.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>